      "author": "YzYhhhstudy",
      "description": "First public release.\n\n- Obsidian plugin (desktop + mobile): sidebar deadline panel with search/stars, `ddl-radar` in-note code-block boards, frontmatter `conference:` countdown banners on paper notes, status-bar badge, startup reminders, insert-table command. English default, 中文 available in settings.\n- Also in this repo: website/PWA with webcal calendar feeds, Chrome/Edge extension (in store review), CLI on npm (`npx ddl-radar`), Raycast and menu-bar clients — all driven by the same open dataset.\n\nThe plugin's only network request is the public, read-only dataset: https://yzyhhhstudy.github.io/paper-deadlines/data.json",
